iGLKit Project implements the IOS 5.0 GLKit framework for IOS 4.2+ and xcode 4.2+.  Implementation uses the header files of GLKit framework.

Current status:
- xcode 4.2 opengl template now working without framework
- further lighting test requires
- further tests on textures, fog, shader program
- per-pixel lighting is missing
- two sided light model is missing
- skybox and reflection map effects are missing
- status of matrix stack, unknown
- optimizations requires